<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentc4846811d3d24acea38e8371948dfb30">
</div>
<p>New Hall Hospital (part of Ramsay Health Care UK) is one of the leading <a href="http://www.newhallhospital.co.uk/about-us" target="_blank" title="Private Hospitals in Salisbury">private hospitals</a> in Salisbury providing a wide range of treatments and diagnostic procedures for both private and NHS patients.</p>
<p>The hospital has 46 beds within 26 single rooms and three double rooms for inpatient stays, together with a two-bed high dependency unit. New Hall Hospital has recently undergone a £4 million refurbishement with a new <a href="http://www.newhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/back-and-spinal-care" target="_blank" title="Spinal surgery in Salisbury">spinal</a> theatre complex and dedicated day case unit.</p>
<p>Our Consultants and nursing staff are highly experienced and have your care and comfort as their highest priority. All our facilities are regularly inspected by the Care Quality Commission.</p>
<p>We provide a range of procedures including <a href="http://www.newhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/ophthalmology" target="_blank" title="Cataract Surgery in Salisbury">cataract</a>, <a href="http://www.newhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/orthopaedics" target="_blank" title="Orthopaedic surgery in Salisbury">orthopaedic</a>, <a href="http://www.newhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/cosmetic-surgery" target="_blank" title="Cosmetic Surgery in Salisbury">cosmetic</a> and <a href="http://www.newhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/varicose-veins" target="_blank" title="Varicose Veins Surgery in Salisbury">veins</a> surgery.</p>
